oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Okeh Records unreleased masters - Wade Ward - 1925-09-01
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: First recording contains unreleased masters of performances by Wade Ward (performer) under Okeh records on September 1, 1925. Second recording contains performances by Chas Higgins (performers), J. Dunevant (performer), C. Cox (performer) [according to tape case] on January 5, 1950.
